    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade E46 M3, a definitive example of atmospheric engineering. This specimen features the legendary S54B32 inline-six, exhibiting perfect compression across all cylinders with the high-pressure VANOS system recently overhauled for optimal cam timing. The drivetrain is anchored by a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance is fully documented, including rod bearing replacement and a comprehensive rear subframe reinforcement using structural epoxy and plates. The chassis retains its factory rigidity, supported by an OEM suspension refresh and staggered Style 67 wheels. Finished in original Carbon Black Metallic with a flawless interior, this M3 represents a rare opportunity to own a mechanically synchronized, high-revving icon in its purest form.",
