      "description": "Presenting a truly remarkable vehicle that stands as a testament to meticulous ownership. This car is in showroom condition, featuring a deep, lustrous paint finish protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating\u2014absolutely free of rock chips, door dings, or swirl marks. The interior is equally breathtaking; the premium leather upholstery remains taut and supple, still carrying that distinct new-car aroma, while the dashboard and trim are devoid of any sun fading or scratches. Every electronic feature, from the premium sound system to the advanced driver-assist suite, functions with factory precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is spotless, reflecting a rigorous maintenance schedule performed exclusively by certified technicians. This car has been climate-control garage-kept and has never seen a drop of rain or snow. It comes complete with a full binder of service records, all original keys, and the factory window sticker. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
